{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"21e26d6576","title":"中共中央关于“三反”运动中对干部撤职及开除处分批准权问题给东北局的批复","origin":"根据文件的翻印件打印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"be3fcf2eab","index":0,"year":1952,"month":3,"day":20,"articleId":"21e26d6576"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"679fbbda50","type":"title","text":"中共中央关于“三反”运动中对干部撤职及开除处分批准权问题给东北局的批复","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"21e26d6576"},{"id":"890e130bb5","type":"appellation","text":"东北局：","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"21e26d6576"},{"id":"dc3b9e7aa9","type":"paragraph","text":"三月十八日电悉。同意在“三反”运动中关于对干部撤职及开除处分的报批手续，按中央过去规定的人事任免管理制度执行。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"21e26d6576"},{"id":"124703b99c","type":"paragraph","text":" 中  央一九五二年三月二十日","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"21e26d6576"},{"id":"dbe9097dbe","type":"appellation","text":"附：","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"21e26d6576"},{"id":"3355abc5b8","type":"subtitle","text":"东北局关于撤职及开除处分批准权问题的请示","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"21e26d6576"},{"id":"2c2ee55825","type":"subtitle","text":"（一九五二年三月十八日）","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"21e26d6576"},{"id":"f46263a624","type":"appellation","text":"中央：","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"21e26d6576"},{"id":"11c9140141","type":"paragraph","text":"政务院三月十一日公布的《关于处理贪污浪费及克服官僚主义错误的若干规定》第四项，其中规定“撤职及开除处分应隔两级批准”。为执行这一规定并简化与统一报批手续，我们建议按中央过去规定的人事任免管理制度执行，即撤职及开除处分的批准属于有权批准任免的机关。妥否，请批示。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"21e26d6576"},{"id":"460e2c04dd","type":"paragraph","text":" 东北局三月十八日","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"21e26d6576"}],"page":{"id":"8b3628c512","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","artic